# ── OWIsMind — repository ignore rules ───────────────────────────────────────
# Philosophy: the plugin SOURCE is tracked, build INPUTS that can be reinstalled
# and build OUTPUTS that can be regenerated are not. One deliberate exception:
# Plugin/owismind/resource/owismind-app/ (the built frontend) IS tracked — it is
# the plugin payload, and the NO-INSTALL policy means a fresh clone cannot rebuild
# it, so it must ship in the repo to stay packageable. Never hand-edit it; rebuild
# it with the build-plugin skill.

# ── Node / frontend toolchain (reinstallable) ────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

# ── Python bytecode ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# ── Packaged deliverable (regenerated by the package-plugin skill) ───────────
Plugin/ready-for-dataiku/

# ── Local build / screenshot scratch (never part of the repo) ────────────────
*-screens/
.vite/
/tmp_build/

# ── OS / editor noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.sw?

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Claude Code local overrides (keep settings.json + skills tracked) ────────
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── Graphify knowledge graph (regenerated by /graphify) ──────────────────────
graphify-out/
